Dialogue: 0,00:20:34.51,00:20:37.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（キバ）こっちへ合流しろってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to join you here!
